api_list.description: The [PRO71](https://pro71.ae/) REST API provides an interface for applications to interact with the [PRO71](https://pro71.ae/) site by sending and receiving data as JSON (JavaScript Object Notation) objects.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://pro71.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "pro71.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
